#ROOMS
#8800
Aeris' Office~
A profound sense of calm infuses you as you enter the home of the Child
Goddess, Aeris.  The walls of this room are marble, and threaded with gold. 
Ivy climbs around the massive support pillars, softening the cold exterior
with both its colour and scent.  Looking through the windows there is a
perfect view of Bal Harbour.  Many mirrors decorate the walls of this room,
a different part of town visible through each glowing portal.  In the centre
of the room is a large polished oak desk, behind that a comfortable looking
arm chair, apholstered in red.  There is a glowing orb floating above the
desk, and a shiney looking Laptop Computer sits closed on the wood.  
~
